parameters:
Is that your hobby? Or did someone tear your
clothes off? If they were torn, it's best to talk
to the shrine maiden in the adjacent confessional
room.

You have been completely impregnated by a demon...
However, if you don't wake up, I won't be able to
treat you. For now, all we can do is wait.
It seems you have awakened, Savior-sama.
Huh?! Are you Kuropan's dad?! Why are you here?

(Huh? Who is Kuropan again? I've heard the name
before, but I can't remember.)
S-Sorry, it seems like I'm still confused.

It seems that due to the influence of your
reincarnation, you are still uncertain. It must
have been a quite unusual reincarnation...

Reincarnation... (I see... I came here for some
reason... Someone was talking about something, I
think...)

What about the other injured people? It seems like
the town has been quite damaged.

There is no need to worry, while you were asleep,
the town has almost fully recovered.

Huh? How long was I asleep for? How long was I
asleep for?
It's been about three whole days...
Three days... I slept that long.

Thank you for bringing me here when I fainted, I
want to express my gratitude.

No need for thanks! You were the one who saved us
from that crisis! It is us who should be
expressing gratitude, not you.

I apologize for the delay. I am the master of this
Magical Girl Guild, and my name is Guild Leader
Gilcho.

Normally, everyone calls me Gilcho casually, so
please feel free to do so... By the way, do you...
remember your name?

I am... Konoha. Yes, it's Konoha. Nice to meet
you, Gilcho. There are a lot of things I want to
ask...

Konoha, that's a nice name! Well then, Konoha-
chan, I would like to ask you something if you
don't mind...

I have to go back to my workplace for a moment, so
can I ask you to hear the details there?
I see. Of course, I don't mind staying here...

This is the medical facility located in the
basement of the guild. I am usually at the
reception on the first floor, so please feel free
to come and see me.
